data.description: Home builder or investor purchase. First time on the market! This two story, 4 bedroom, 3 bath, plus office / cabana room, was custom built in 1989 on a large 12k sq. ft. lot plus an FPL easement in the backyard extending the backyard another 25-30 feet. Fenced in backyard includes a free-form pool and covered patio.  Roof is 3 months old. Sold AS-IS. New Construction homes in the neighborhood starting at $2.799M. Addison Mizner / Boca Middle & Boca High school district. BRING YOUR OFFERS! Please send proof of funds with all written offers.
